{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                                         // hydrogen // schema"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | # Hydrogen Design System Schema"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | A comprehensive ontology for digital design, built for:"},{"LineComment":" | - **Human designers** who need precise, professional terminology"},{"LineComment":" | - **AI agents** (COMPASS, Devin, etc.) who need machine-readable schemas"},{"LineComment":" | - **Visual tools** that export brand configurations as PureScript code"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## The 12 Pillars"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | The schema is organized into 12 top-level domains (pillars), each covering"},{"LineComment":" | a fundamental aspect of digital design. Pillars are designed to be:"},{"LineComment":" | - **Composable** - combine types from multiple pillars"},{"LineComment":" | - **Serializable** - JSON encode/decode for agent consumption"},{"LineComment":" | - **Semantically precise** - professional terminology matters"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 1. Color"},{"LineComment":" | Color science, theory, and application."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Spaces**: sRGB, Linear RGB, Display P3, Adobe RGB, ACES, CMYK, LAB, OKLAB, HSL, HSV, HSB, LCH, OKLCH"},{"LineComment":" | - **Theory**: Harmony (complementary, triadic, analogous), temperature (warm/cool), value, chroma, hue"},{"LineComment":" | - **Grading**: LUTs (1D, 3D), curves (RGB, luminance), lift/gamma/gain, ASC-CDL"},{"LineComment":" | - **3D/PBR**: Albedo, specular, metallic, roughness, emissive, subsurface"},{"LineComment":" | - **Maps**: Diffuse, normal, ambient occlusion, displacement, mask, alpha"},{"LineComment":" | - **Blending**: Porter-Duff compositing, standard blend modes, mix/lerp"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 2. Dimension"},{"LineComment":" | Measurement, spacing, and layout."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Units**: Pixels, rem, em, viewport units, percentages, fr, ch"},{"LineComment":" | - **Scale**: Spacing scale (none/xs/sm/md/lg/xl/2xl/...), sizing scale"},{"LineComment":" | - **Layout**: Grid (columns, rows, gap, areas), flexbox, flow"},{"LineComment":" | - **Responsive**: Breakpoints, container queries, media queries"},{"LineComment":" | - **Zones**: Regions, heatmaps, attention mapping, safe areas"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 3. Geometry"},{"LineComment":" | Shape, form, and spatial transformation."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Primitives**: Rectangle, circle, ellipse, polygon, line"},{"LineComment":" | - **Radius**: Corner radius (uniform, per-corner), squircle/superellipse"},{"LineComment":" | - **Paths**: Bezier curves, SVG path data, splines"},{"LineComment":" | - **Clipping**: Clip paths, masks, insets, polygon masks"},{"LineComment":" | - **Transforms**: Translate, rotate, scale, skew, matrix, transform-origin"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 4. Typography"},{"LineComment":" | Text rendering and typographic hierarchy."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Families**: System stacks, web fonts, variable fonts, font fallbacks"},{"LineComment":" | - **Scale**: Type scale (xs/sm/base/lg/xl/2xl/...), modular scales"},{"LineComment":" | - **Weight**: Hairline to black (100-900), variable weight"},{"LineComment":" | - **Style**: Italic, oblique, small-caps, font-features"},{"LineComment":" | - **Case**: Uppercase, lowercase, capitalize, small-caps"},{"LineComment":" | - **Decoration**: Underline, strikethrough, emphasis marks"},{"LineComment":" | - **Hierarchy**: Display, heading, body, caption, overline, code"},{"LineComment":" | - **Rhythm**: Line height, letter spacing, word spacing, optical sizing"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 5. Material"},{"LineComment":" | Surface appearance and texture."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Fill**: Solid, linear gradient, radial gradient, conic gradient, pattern"},{"LineComment":" | - **Texture**: Noise (perlin, simplex, worley), procedural, image-based"},{"LineComment":" | - **Effects**: Glassmorphism, neumorphism, frosted glass, blur"},{"LineComment":" | - **Borders**: Width, style (solid, dashed, dotted), image borders"},{"LineComment":" | - **Finish**: Matte, glossy, metallic, satin, textured"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 6. Elevation"},{"LineComment":" | Depth, shadow, and visual hierarchy."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Shadows**: Box shadow (offset, blur, spread, color), drop shadow, inner shadow"},{"LineComment":" | - **Scale**: Elevation levels (0-24 or semantic: flat/raised/floating/modal)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Perspective**: Vanishing point, FOV, depth of field"},{"LineComment":" | - **Parallax**: Scroll-linked depth, layer velocity"},{"LineComment":" | - **Stacking**: Z-index management, isolation, stacking contexts"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 7. Temporal"},{"LineComment":" | Time, motion, and animation."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Duration**: Instant, fast, normal, slow, glacial (semantic scale)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Easing**: Linear, ease, cubic-bezier, spring physics, custom curves"},{"LineComment":" | - **Transitions**: Property transitions, enter/exit, cross-fade"},{"LineComment":" | - **Keyframes**: Animation sequences, percentage-based, named"},{"LineComment":" | - **Orchestration**: Stagger, sequence, parallel, timeline"},{"LineComment":" | - **External**: Lottie, Rive, GSAP, Framer Motion integration points"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 8. Reactive"},{"LineComment":" | State and feedback."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Interactive**: Default, hover, focus, focus-visible, active, visited, disabled"},{"LineComment":" | - **Semantic**: Loading, success, error, warning, info, pending"},{"LineComment":" | - **Data**: Empty, populated, partial, stale, refreshing"},{"LineComment":" | - **Validation**: Valid, invalid, pristine, dirty, touched"},{"LineComment":" | - **Feedback**: Toast, notification, inline, modal"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 9. Gestural"},{"LineComment":" | User input and interaction patterns."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Pointer**: Click, double-click, right-click, hover, drag"},{"LineComment":" | - **Touch**: Tap, double-tap, long-press, swipe, pinch, rotate"},{"LineComment":" | - **Scroll**: Scroll, overscroll, scroll-snap, infinite scroll"},{"LineComment":" | - **Drag**: Drag-and-drop, reorder, resize handles"},{"LineComment":" | - **Keyboard**: Focus management, shortcuts, key sequences"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 10. Haptic"},{"LineComment":" | Tactile and sensory feedback."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Vibration**: Impact (light/medium/heavy), notification, selection"},{"LineComment":" | - **Force**: 3D Touch, pressure sensitivity, force feedback"},{"LineComment":" | - **Audio**: Click sounds, notification sounds, ambient"},{"LineComment":" | - **Tactile**: Surface texture simulation, resistance"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 11. Spatial"},{"LineComment":" | 3D and extended reality."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Scene**: Camera, lighting, environment maps, skybox"},{"LineComment":" | - **Objects**: Mesh, material, geometry, instancing"},{"LineComment":" | - **AR**: Surface detection, anchors, occlusion, lighting estimation"},{"LineComment":" | - **VR**: Head tracking, hand tracking, room-scale, teleportation"},{"LineComment":" | - **Mixed**: Pass-through, spatial UI, world-locked content"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### 12. Brand"},{"LineComment":" | Identity and theming."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Tokens**: Design tokens (primitive, semantic, component)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Themes**: Light, dark, high-contrast, color-blind modes"},{"LineComment":" | - **Voice**: Tone, personality, microcopy style"},{"LineComment":" | - **Assets**: Logos, icons, illustrations, photography style"},{"LineComment":" | - **Composition**: How pillars combine into a cohesive system"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Pillars may have overlapping semantic names (e.g., `lg`, `md`, `sm` appear in"},{"LineComment":" | multiple pillars). Always use qualified imports:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Color as Color"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Dimension as Dimension"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Typography as Type"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | myColor :: Color.Value"},{"LineComment":" | myColor = Color.hex \"#3b82f6\""},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | mySpacing :: Dimension.Length"},{"LineComment":" | mySpacing = Dimension.rem 1.5"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## For AI Agents"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This schema is designed to be consumed by AI agents for:"},{"LineComment":" | - **Code generation**: Generate type-safe PureScript from natural language"},{"LineComment":" | - **Design validation**: Check designs against brand guidelines"},{"LineComment":" | - **Theme creation**: Build complete themes from partial specifications"},{"LineComment":" | - **Component styling**: Apply consistent styling to UI components"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | All types are serializable to JSON for agent consumption."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Import Pattern"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Do NOT import this module directly. Import pillars with qualification:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Color as Color"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Color.Hue as Hue"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Color.Saturation as Saturation"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Dimension as Dimension"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This module exists for documentation only."}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[171,29],"start":[171,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema.purs","reExports":{},"sourceSpan":{"end":[171,29],"start":[171,1]}}